  "id": "RAW_c34427d4",
  "title": "重磅！DeepSeek V3.2 特别版发布：性能超越 GPT-5，硬刚 Gemini 3.0「IOI/IMO 金牌」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==&mid=2247510326&idx=1&sn=358022adbc8257bb72e5fefb2026418b",
  "date": "2025-12-01 12:02:00",
  "author": "AI寒武纪",
