  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100026659\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=098da2c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0U9bsmPQNnX5oicJKMXRnjPDBzgP4Vg37HLrqjR1Kwl5ToWtTSdoSCZcQt6gTFXuyfMsH2FlSvPwqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AI寒武纪\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ICgnAptln0Xg6w3lVHUFXrtY5Tia7rfUDkTmCwe5Gz5RRAtVR2CX6UgcZiaFWnxksH1fkSSmjxichSCic8CTGqcElA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"一起见证人工智能的寒武纪大爆发，传播一切有关AI的技术\" data-id=\"Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">↑阅读之前记得关注+星标⭐️，😄，每天才能第一时间接收到更新</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-top:0px !important;margin-bottom:1.5em;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2系列模型正式上线</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为“为Agent构建的推理优先模型”，DeepSeek-V3.2包含两个版本：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：V3.2-Exp的官方继任者，平衡了推理能力与生成长度，性能对标GPT-5，现已上线App、Web端及API</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：专攻深度推理能力的极限版本，性能超越GPT-5，比肩Gemini-3.0-Pro，目前仅通过API提供</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100026661\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0fc3f164&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FICgnAptln0U9bsmPQNnX5oicJKMXRnjPDnicXojw0icHLUeIo5AYdS0axnPh5RBnU0V1PLegPoazvjbV0Rn0DMR6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术报告显示，DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale在2025年国际数学奥林匹克（IMO）、国际信息学奥林匹克（IOI）、ICPC世界总决赛及CMO中均取得了</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">金牌级</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">成绩</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100026662\" data-ratio=\"0.6027777777777777\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a17df5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FICgnAptln0U9bsmPQNnX5oicJKMXRnjPDHbTr6O5K6SdUI4Poh1WricltYrQOic2Re5FA6OZ5kNyqXjE7YUlgrp0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方已公开上述竞赛的最终提交结果，社区可通过</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">assets/olympiad_cases</span></code><span leaf=\"\">进行二次验证</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100026658\" data-ratio=\"0.6953703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e12c586&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0U9bsmPQNnX5oicJKMXRnjPDl2dicU54fRGIwuTibS841lIAMjaiasGgnoGltzXZclGahHibybia4xibc8EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术报告：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.2/blob/main/assets/paper.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.2/blob/main/assets/paper.pdf</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100026660\" data-ratio=\"0.8296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44174c9a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0U9bsmPQNnX5oicJKMXRnjPDyshicG4pjebomQhvXKzj34hhvIOVeKdpcrw7K2xo1ZaGuZdicFRPQ1Hg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">以下是详细信息</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心能力与技术突破</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2基于三大技术突破，实现了高计算效率与卓越推理、Agent性能的统一：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.DeepSeek Sparse Attention (DSA)：引入高效注意力机制，大幅降低计算复杂度，并针对长上下文场景进行了优化</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.可扩展强化学习框架：通过稳健的RL协议与后训练（post-training）算力扩展，实现了高性能表现</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.大规模Agent任务合成管线：涵盖1800+环境及8.5万+复杂指令</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一合成管线不仅提升了模型在复杂交互环境中的遵循度和泛化能力，更让DeepSeek-V3.2将“思考”直接整合进工具使用（Tool-Use）的模型，同时支持在思考和非思考模式下使用工具</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.21203703703703702\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100026663\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8e1c655e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FICgnAptln0U9bsmPQNnX5oicJKMXRnjPD23kFSMjQ5DQMoPpszUTaPibaCXXn9Nly1YPESTJ12ltia6pcnE8Em2pA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">API更新与Speciale版限制</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">API使用模式与V3.2-Exp保持一致，作为日常主力模型（Daily Driver），提供GPT-5级别的性能</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">该版本专为解决复杂任务设计，消耗更多Token，目前仅作为API提供，具体限制如下：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">临时端点</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：需使用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">base_url=\"<a href=\"https://api.deepseek.com/v3.2_speciale_expires_on_20251215\" target=\"_blank\">https://api.deepseek.com/v3.2_speciale_expires_on_20251215</a>\"</span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">服务期限：该端点服务至</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年12月15日 15:59 (UTC)</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;截止</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">功能限制：不支持工具调用（Tool Calls），仅用于支持社区评估与研究。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">定价：与DeepSeek-V3.2保持一致</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">聊天模板重大调整</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-V3.2不再提供Jinja格式模板，并引入了“带工具思考”及新角色设定。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Python脚本编码</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：官方提供了</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">encoding</span></code><span leaf=\"\">文件夹，包含Python脚本（</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">encoding_dsv32.py</span></code><span leaf=\"\">），用于将OpenAI兼容格式消息编码为模型输入字符串及解析输出</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Developer角色</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：模板新增</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">developer</span></code><span leaf=\"\">角色，专门用于搜索Agent场景，官方API不接受分配给该角色的消息</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">输出解析注意</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：提供的解析函数仅处理格式良好的字符串，生产环境需自行增加稳健的错误处理机制。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码示例如下：</span></p>\n    <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;text-align:justify;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0.5em 1em 1em;margin:0px;text-indent:0px;white-space:nowrap;display:-webkit-box;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;transformers</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">from</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;encoding_dsv32</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;import</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;encode_messages</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">tokenizer = transformers.AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(</span><span><span leaf=\"\">\"deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.2\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">messages = [</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; {</span><span><span leaf=\"\">\"role\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"user\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"content\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"hello\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">},</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; {</span><span><span leaf=\"\">\"role\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"assistant\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"content\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"Hello! I am DeepSeek.\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"reasoning_content\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"thinking...\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">},</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; {</span><span><span leaf=\"\">\"role\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"user\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"content\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"1+1=?\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">}</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">]</span><span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"># 思考模式配置</span></span><span leaf=\"\">encode_config =</span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;dict</span></span><span leaf=\"\">(thinking_mode=</span><span><span leaf=\"\">\"thinking\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">, drop_thinking=</span><span><span leaf=\"\">True</span></span><span leaf=\"\">, add_default_bos_token=</span><span><span leaf=\"\">True</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">prompt = encode_messages(messages, **encode_config)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">tokens = tokenizer.encode(prompt)</span></code></pre>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">本地部署建议</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型结构与DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp相同。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">采样参数</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：建议设置 temperature = 1.0，top_p = 0.95。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Speciale版提示</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：本地部署Speciale版本时，同样不支持工具调用功能</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源与协议</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">仓库及模型权重均采用&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">MIT License</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;授权。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">--end--</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepSeek 发布 V3.2 系列大语言模型，其中 Speciale 版在奥赛中取得金牌级成绩，性能超越 GPT-5，并开源了核心技术与 API，专为 Agent 构建优化。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepSeek 发布 V3.2 系列大语言模型，其中 Speciale 版在奥赛中取得金牌级成绩，性能超越 GPT-5，并开源了核心技术与 API，专为 Agent 构建优化。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 DeepSeek V3.2 系列大型语言模型的发布，包括平衡推理与生成长度的 DeepSeek-V3.2，以及专攻深度推理的 DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale。Speciale 版取得了令人瞩目的成就，声称在 2025 年国际数学奥林匹克（IMO）、国际信息学奥林匹克（IOI）等竞赛中斩获金牌级成绩，其性能据称超越 GPT-5，并能比肩 Gemini-3.0-Pro。文章深入阐述了模型背后的三大核心技术突破：DeepSeek Sparse Attention（大幅降低计算复杂度）、可扩展强化学习框架和大规模 Agent 任务合成管线，这些创新共同显著提升了模型的计算效率、卓越推理能力及在复杂 Agent 场景下的性能。此外，文章还详细提供了 DeepSeek-V3.2 系列模型的 API 使用指南、聊天模板的重大调整说明（引入'带工具思考'模式和新角色设定），以及本地部署的建议配置。最后，文章强调了模型仓库及权重均采用 MIT License 授权，体现了其对开源社区的贡献，为开发者和研究者提供了丰富的资源和工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek V3.2 Speciale 版在奥赛中表现卓越，性能超越 GPT-5。",
      "explanation": "该版本在 IMO、IOI 等国际竞赛中获得金牌级成绩，展示了其在深度推理和复杂问题解决方面的领先能力，为 Agent 构建提供了强大基础。"
